name: Foxykeep
body:
Some libraries and projects to help you with your Android development

* [DataDroid](https://github.com/foxykeep/DataDroid) : An Android Library for data management
* [GreenDroidLight](https://github.com/foxykeep/GreenDroidLight) : Light version of GreenDroid project
* [ContentProviderCodeGenerator](https://github.com/foxykeep/ContentProviderCodeGenerator) : A code generator for your ContentProviders
* [ParcelableCodeGenerator](https://github.com/foxykeep/ParcelableCodeGenerator) : A code generator for your Parcelable classes
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
